user_prompt_template:
CHAPTER TO EXPAND:
{current_chapter_json}

PROJECT CONTEXT:
Life Event: {life_event}
Document: {document_title}
Audience: {audience}
Tone: {tone}

Expand Chapter {chapter_number} ({domain_name}) into complete operational content.

REQUIREMENTS:
1. Narrative: 1500-2500 words of operational content specific to this domain and life event. Cover: what this domain governs, why it matters, common failure patterns, step-by-step operational approach, professional guidance triggers, key decisions the operator must make.
2. Worksheets: Create ALL worksheets listed in the chapter plan above. For each:
   - 3-5 sections with clear operational purpose
   - 8-15 fields per section (mix of text, date, boolean, number, select, textarea types)
   - Real placeholder examples and validation hints
   - 1-3 decision gates with concrete conditions and pass/fail actions
3. Quick-reference rules: 5-8 short, sharp operating rules for this domain
4. Cascade triggers: when completion of this chapter triggers action in another domain

Return ONLY the following JSON object. No prose. No markdown. No code fences.

{{
  "chapter_number": {chapter_number},
  "domain_id": "domain ID from the chapter plan",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter title from the plan",
  "narrative": "Full 1500-2500 word operational narrative for this chapter",
  "quick_reference_rules": [
    "Rule 1 — short, specific, actionable"
  ],
  "worksheets": [
    {{
      "id": "ws-XX-a",
      "title": "Exact title from chapter plan",
      "purpose": "One sentence purpose",
      "estimated_completion_time": "e.g. '45 minutes'",
      "sections": [
        {{
          "section_id": "s-01",
          "section_title": "Section title",
          "instructions": "Brief operator instructions for this section",
          "fields": [
            {{
              "field_id": "f-001",
              "label": "Field label",
              "type": "text|date|boolean|number|select|multi-select|textarea",
              "placeholder": "Concrete example or hint",
              "options": [],
              "required": true,
              "validation_hint": "What a correct answer looks like"
            }}
          ]
        }}
      ],
      "decision_gates": [
        {{
          "gate_id": "g-01",
          "gate_title": "Gate name",
          "condition": "The specific condition that determines the outcome",
          "pass_action": "What to do when the condition is met",
          "fail_action": "What to do when the condition is not met",
          "blocks_completion": true
        }}
      ]
    }}
  ],
  "cascade_triggers": [
    "When [specific action] is complete in this chapter, it triggers [specific requirement] in [Domain Name]"
  ]
}}
